So you raise to 2@H on your 3 card suit

There are ways opener can ask if you  have 3 or 4 card support, but that's too much stuff for this evening.. 
Anyway, because opener is distributional to bid 1@H over 1@D, 
your raise rates to work better more often that bidding 1@S will. 

